      "title": "[正面] Started to play with the 2.0 as a F2P and I'm real...",
      "summary": "Started to play with the 2.0 as a F2P and I'm really enjoying the game, the style and animation are very nice, and the roguelike-style gameplay is pretty fun.\nYes, the machine translation is not the best, but even if English is not my first language, I'm managing to understand and appreciate the story so far.\nI recommend trying it for a bit, doing the story, and gaining some level to unlock new rewards and game mechanics and make your opinion.\nPretty good.",
